      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything i worked for... it’s just gone. the person everyone thought i was, the person i actually liked... they don't exist anymore. it feels like that version of me is actually dead. like there's nothing left in this body but a hollow shell. i don't know why i'm even still here.",
