    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"rest\" feels like such a small word for what i actually need. i don't want to just sit in the dark and wait for things to get better, because they won't. that person is gone forever. it feels like the only way to actually be at peace with that is to just... let it go completely. to not have to carry this shell around anymore. wouldn't it be easier if everything just stopped?",
